1
00:00:19,690 --> 00:00:26,890
♪Lights of swords are like
a splash of rivers♪

2
00:00:27,280 --> 00:00:34,320
♪Shadows of swords cover the seasons♪

3
00:00:34,700 --> 00:00:38,090
♪The clear water cuts off the gorge♪

4
00:00:38,910 --> 00:00:42,190
♪Which is facing the armed army♪

5
00:00:42,410 --> 00:00:45,780
♪Missing a pot of cold wine♪

6
00:00:46,520 --> 00:00:49,590
♪Drunk in the middle of sand♪

7
00:00:49,670 --> 00:00:53,520
♪The place of peace of mind
is my hometown♪

8
00:00:54,280 --> 00:00:57,240
♪But my hometown is by your side♪

9
00:00:57,240 --> 00:01:01,520
♪Who forgets about the grudges
in the past♪

10
00:01:01,830 --> 00:01:04,920
♪Don’t blame the west wind
for your tears♪

11
00:01:04,920 --> 00:01:08,700
♪To meet and to part are like a dream♪

12
00:01:09,430 --> 00:01:12,610
♪Well-armed with armor and weapons♪

13
00:01:12,610 --> 00:01:16,960
♪Where the surging river is going♪

14
00:01:17,120 --> 00:01:22,960
♪Together we go to the end of the world♪

15
00:01:24,380 --> 00:01:29,980
=Legend of Fei=

16
00:01:30,020 --> 00:01:32,940
=Episode 14=

17
00:01:34,000 --> 00:01:35,680
Let’s get some rest here.

18
00:01:35,680 --> 00:01:37,870
Once Dragon Master and the troops leave,

19
00:01:37,870 --> 00:01:40,190
we can get out and escape.

20
00:01:40,190 --> 00:01:41,210
Escape?

21
00:01:42,120 --> 00:01:43,800
Dragon Master is onto you.

22
00:01:43,800 --> 00:01:46,800
Don’t even dream about escaping.

23
00:01:46,800 --> 00:01:48,310
Dragon Master will hunt you down

24
00:01:48,310 --> 00:01:50,060
no matter where you are.

25
00:01:50,910 --> 00:01:52,760
You think this crappy hideout

26
00:01:52,760 --> 00:01:54,340
can keep him away? Don’t be ridiculous!

27
00:01:55,870 --> 00:01:57,040
Aren’t you his follower?

28
00:01:57,040 --> 00:01:58,120
Wouldn’t he save you?

29
00:01:58,760 --> 00:02:00,550
If he arrives,

30
00:02:00,550 --> 00:02:01,850
I’ll be his first target of murder.

31
00:02:04,910 --> 00:02:06,900
Others take in disciples

32
00:02:07,510 --> 00:02:09,730
while Dragon Master has adopted 18 kids.

33
00:02:10,030 --> 00:02:11,880
I heard others call you “Young Master”.

34
00:02:12,830 --> 00:02:15,320
Don’t flatter me. I’m ashamed of it.

35
00:02:16,320 --> 00:02:17,880
Don’t you know

36
00:02:17,880 --> 00:02:19,480
even dogs

37
00:02:19,830 --> 00:02:20,800
have names, too?

38
00:02:21,830 --> 00:02:23,440
Each time we see him,

39
00:02:23,440 --> 00:02:25,530
we can only speak in prostration.

40
00:02:27,440 --> 00:02:29,270
He’s also

41
00:02:30,100 --> 00:02:31,980
marked all of us.

42
00:02:33,320 --> 00:02:35,080
Where’s your mark?

43
00:02:36,550 --> 00:02:38,830
Didn’t you see that big mark?

44
00:02:38,830 --> 00:02:40,680
You should be ashamed.

45
00:02:42,390 --> 00:02:43,720
You can say that again.

46
00:02:43,720 --> 00:02:45,050
Be that as it may,

47
00:02:45,550 --> 00:02:47,510
I’m the smartest and most obedient

48
00:02:47,880 --> 00:02:48,830
people pleaser.

49
00:02:49,880 --> 00:02:52,500
So he always takes me with him.

50
00:02:53,720 --> 00:02:56,800
Old Dragon was too dull

51
00:02:57,910 --> 00:03:00,690
to be anywhere near Master,

52
00:03:01,110 --> 00:03:04,030
so he could only swallow his pride

53
00:03:04,030 --> 00:03:05,300
and suck up to me.

54
00:03:06,030 --> 00:03:07,540
That’s why I took him

55
00:03:08,440 --> 00:03:09,600
to take care of that old fart.

56
00:03:12,190 --> 00:03:16,030
Supposedly,

57
00:03:16,030 --> 00:03:17,680
it wouldn’t take him too long.

58
00:03:18,240 --> 00:03:19,370
But we didn’t expect

59
00:03:20,000 --> 00:03:21,740
the North Blade

60
00:03:22,190 --> 00:03:23,710
had help.

61
00:03:24,880 --> 00:03:25,710
You’re good!

62
00:03:33,030 --> 00:03:34,760
You killed Old Dragon.

63
00:03:35,880 --> 00:03:37,360
Were it before that I bullied others

64
00:03:37,360 --> 00:03:38,750
and made mistakes,

65
00:03:38,750 --> 00:03:40,420
I’d be whipped and let go.

66
00:03:41,000 --> 00:03:42,040
But this time,

67
00:03:44,270 --> 00:03:48,140
whipping alone wouldn’t be enough.

68
00:03:49,830 --> 00:03:51,210
You’re going to get beaten up.

69
00:04:10,600 --> 00:04:13,040
The South and North Blades
were the Top Two.

70
00:04:14,470 --> 00:04:16,350
Li Zheng was in the south

71
00:04:16,350 --> 00:04:17,820
while Guan Feng was in the north,
hence the titles.

72
00:04:20,000 --> 00:04:21,800
Old Master Li was
well-connected.

73
00:04:22,320 --> 00:04:22,920
He became

74
00:04:22,920 --> 00:04:24,950
a household name

75
00:04:24,950 --> 00:04:25,940
because of the Fortress
of the Forty-Eight.

76
00:04:27,480 --> 00:04:28,440
On the contrary,

77
00:04:28,440 --> 00:04:29,440
Mr. Guan, Guan Feng,

78
00:04:29,440 --> 00:04:31,200
was less engaged

79
00:04:31,200 --> 00:04:33,450
although he was ten years older.

80
00:04:34,200 --> 00:04:36,280
There were stories
about him in the past,

81
00:04:36,880 --> 00:04:38,950
but ever since that armed rebellion,

82
00:04:38,950 --> 00:04:40,080
he never came to Central Plains again

83
00:04:40,600 --> 00:04:42,130
and only existed in stories.

84
00:04:46,720 --> 00:04:49,070
My mother once told me about them.

85
00:04:50,480 --> 00:04:52,520
The South Blade was cold

86
00:04:53,320 --> 00:04:54,970
as the snowstorm

87
00:04:55,550 --> 00:04:58,980
while the North Blade
could cut off water.

88
00:04:59,390 --> 00:05:01,610
The North Blade was fierce.

89
00:05:02,270 --> 00:05:03,830
Yes, he was,

90
00:05:03,830 --> 00:05:05,870
fierce and shameless.

91
00:05:09,320 --> 00:05:10,640
At that time,

92
00:05:11,480 --> 00:05:12,660
I believed I was skilled enough

93
00:05:13,670 --> 00:05:16,260
to leave for Central Plains.

94
00:05:17,200 --> 00:05:18,800
My master didn’t want me to,

95
00:05:20,000 --> 00:05:22,170
but I thought he was timid

96
00:05:23,040 --> 00:05:23,960
and old.

97
00:05:24,920 --> 00:05:25,820
I didn’t listen to him.

98
00:05:28,760 --> 00:05:30,680
Seeing that he couldn’t change my mind,

99
00:05:31,920 --> 00:05:35,440
he told me over and over before I left

100
00:05:35,440 --> 00:05:37,540
to always think twice.

101
00:05:39,070 --> 00:05:39,820
He said,

102
00:05:40,830 --> 00:05:41,800
“look,

103
00:05:43,390 --> 00:05:44,880
your blade

104
00:05:45,760 --> 00:05:48,330
is similar to a farmer’s hoe

105
00:05:49,040 --> 00:05:50,830
and an accountant’s abacus.

106
00:05:52,270 --> 00:05:56,120
Both are to get things done,

107
00:05:56,670 --> 00:05:58,510
not to gain fame and wealth.

108
00:05:59,480 --> 00:06:02,530
Do not mistake it”.

109
00:06:04,040 --> 00:06:07,090
How is a blade equal to
a hoe or an abacus?

110
00:06:07,800 --> 00:06:09,780
I didn’t get it either,

111
00:06:10,440 --> 00:06:11,920
so I ignored it.

112
00:06:13,480 --> 00:06:14,490
I thought

113
00:06:15,200 --> 00:06:17,390
a blade is a weapon.

114
00:06:17,390 --> 00:06:19,990
It has a soul

115
00:06:21,000 --> 00:06:23,390
that connects mine

116
00:06:23,390 --> 00:06:26,220
as if it were part of my body.

117
00:06:27,320 --> 00:06:30,750
How could it be compared
with a lifeless tool?

118
00:06:43,480 --> 00:06:44,900
After I arrived in Central Plains,

119
00:06:45,390 --> 00:06:46,260
soon,

120
00:06:47,200 --> 00:06:49,350
I made a name of myself

121
00:06:49,350 --> 00:06:51,600
by this blade.

122
00:06:51,600 --> 00:06:52,940
I was proud

123
00:06:53,790 --> 00:06:54,700
and I planned

124
00:06:55,720 --> 00:06:57,970
to start my own sect

125
00:06:58,640 --> 00:07:00,670
to revitalize the North Blade.

126
00:07:01,830 --> 00:07:03,030
Within six months,

127
00:07:03,600 --> 00:07:05,110
I challenged seven masters

128
00:07:05,110 --> 00:07:06,790
and beat them all

129
00:07:07,440 --> 00:07:08,190
until...

130
00:07:13,160 --> 00:07:14,390
Soon after the North Blade,
Ji Yunchen, arrived,

131
00:07:14,390 --> 00:07:16,920
he defeated seven masters in a row.

132
00:07:16,920 --> 00:07:18,480
So far, he hasn’t lost once.

133
00:07:18,480 --> 00:07:19,670
He’s really something!

134
00:07:19,670 --> 00:07:21,830
He hasn’t challenged Mr. Yin.

135
00:07:21,880 --> 00:07:22,920
You know what?

136
00:07:22,920 --> 00:07:26,270
His master holed up

137
00:07:26,270 --> 00:07:28,390
far away from Central Plains for so long

138
00:07:28,390 --> 00:07:29,070
because

139
00:07:29,070 --> 00:07:30,970
he had lost to the Mountain Sword,
Yin Wenlan.

140
00:07:31,720 --> 00:07:32,510
Obviously,

141
00:07:32,510 --> 00:07:34,550
water cutting is nothing.

142
00:07:34,550 --> 00:07:36,320
It doesn’t deserve to be
one of the two Blades

143
00:07:36,320 --> 00:07:38,010
as the Snow-breaking Blade does.

144
00:07:39,110 --> 00:07:40,600
Those rumors can’t be trusted.

145
00:07:40,600 --> 00:07:41,910
I agree.

146
00:07:42,440 --> 00:07:45,300
Where are you going next, Mr. Yan?

147
00:07:45,640 --> 00:07:47,080
Not sure yet.

148
00:07:49,920 --> 00:07:50,510
Please enjoy.

149
00:07:50,510 --> 00:07:51,580
Please.

150
00:07:56,860 --> 00:08:10,460
(Yin’s Mansion)

151
00:08:14,760 --> 00:08:15,460
Sir,

152
00:08:17,830 --> 00:08:18,600
you’d better leave.

153
00:08:22,440 --> 00:08:23,240
Yin Wenlan!

154
00:08:23,860 --> 00:08:25,220
(Yin Wenlan, the Mountain Sword)

155
00:08:25,550 --> 00:08:26,940
Are you not up for the challenge?

156
00:08:28,040 --> 00:08:28,580
Fine.

157
00:08:29,200 --> 00:08:31,480
I’ll wait here for three days.

158
00:08:31,480 --> 00:08:33,110
If you don’t come out,

159
00:08:33,110 --> 00:08:34,590
I’ll tell the world

160
00:08:34,590 --> 00:08:37,150
the Mountain Sword is
inferior to the North Blade.

161
00:08:39,910 --> 00:08:40,880
Yin Wenlan!

162
00:08:47,670 --> 00:08:49,590
When my mother was about my age,

163
00:08:49,590 --> 00:08:51,520
she broke into Demons Manor

164
00:08:51,520 --> 00:08:53,200
and battled the top three Demons

165
00:08:53,200 --> 00:08:54,700
together with Duan Jiuniang.

166
00:08:55,470 --> 00:08:57,590
The latter was well-known for her Palm

167
00:08:57,590 --> 00:09:00,140
in her early 20s.

168
00:09:01,000 --> 00:09:02,670
And Mr. Ji

169
00:09:02,670 --> 00:09:04,940
quickly made a name of himself,

170
00:09:05,640 --> 00:09:08,550
planning to set up his own sect.

171
00:09:09,710 --> 00:09:11,100
But what about me?

172
00:09:13,400 --> 00:09:14,060
What’s on your mind?

173
00:09:15,640 --> 00:09:16,520
I think

174
00:09:17,320 --> 00:09:20,880
my weapon is no different

175
00:09:20,880 --> 00:09:22,080
from a blunt tool.

176
00:09:25,590 --> 00:09:27,080
Mr. Ji,

177
00:09:27,080 --> 00:09:28,910
then what happened?

178
00:09:35,220 --> 00:09:41,300
(Yin’s Mansion)

179
00:09:44,550 --> 00:09:45,820
What are you doing here?

180
00:09:46,790 --> 00:09:49,080
Beat it, kid.

181
00:09:49,080 --> 00:09:50,770
I’m not any kid.

182
00:09:51,670 --> 00:09:53,520
The Mountain Sword,

183
00:09:53,520 --> 00:09:55,120
Yin Wenlan, is my father.

184
00:09:55,910 --> 00:09:57,660
You’re Yin Wenlan’s son?

185
00:09:58,440 --> 00:10:00,350
Good. Go home

186
00:10:00,350 --> 00:10:01,110
and tell your father to come out.

187
00:10:01,110 --> 00:10:01,840
No.

188
00:10:01,840 --> 00:10:02,760
Why?

189
00:10:02,760 --> 00:10:04,080
I sneaked out

190
00:10:04,080 --> 00:10:06,430
because I didn’t want to study.

191
00:10:07,590 --> 00:10:08,670
What do you want to do?

192
00:10:08,670 --> 00:10:09,360
Play games.

193
00:10:15,000 --> 00:10:15,450
Alright.

194
00:10:16,200 --> 00:10:17,280
Let’s go

195
00:10:17,280 --> 00:10:18,210
play games.

196
00:10:18,670 --> 00:10:19,760
Once you have enough fun,

197
00:10:19,760 --> 00:10:20,930
I’ll bring you back.

198
00:10:21,440 --> 00:10:22,150
Alright?

199
00:10:23,400 --> 00:10:24,350
This will be

200
00:10:24,400 --> 00:10:25,630
our secret.

201
00:10:26,760 --> 00:10:27,200
Let’s go.

202
00:10:28,030 --> 00:10:28,960
That day,

203
00:10:28,960 --> 00:10:32,640
Guan Feng charged at
Mr. Yin with his blade.

204
00:10:32,640 --> 00:10:34,760
The two fought for 300 rounds.

205
00:10:35,320 --> 00:10:35,870
Everyone,

206
00:10:36,230 --> 00:10:40,060
can you imagine that?

207
00:10:40,790 --> 00:10:42,590
They fought so hard

208
00:10:42,590 --> 00:10:46,000
that the world seemed to
fall apart in darkness.

209
00:10:47,440 --> 00:10:51,080
All that could be seen
were gleaming blades.

210
00:10:51,710 --> 00:10:53,790
Still, Mr. Yin’s skills

211
00:10:53,790 --> 00:10:57,560
were unparalleled, one of a kind.

212
00:10:58,350 --> 00:10:59,720
The Mountain Sword

213
00:11:00,080 --> 00:11:01,180
crushed the North Blade

214
00:11:01,590 --> 00:11:03,080
who lost terribly

215
00:11:03,080 --> 00:11:04,990
and made a fool of himself.

216
00:11:05,440 --> 00:11:08,030
-Yes! Great!
-Good!

217
00:11:08,030 --> 00:11:09,110
Sir,

218
00:11:09,110 --> 00:11:10,640
who’s the North Blade

219
00:11:10,640 --> 00:11:13,150
that lost terribly to my father?

220
00:11:13,150 --> 00:11:16,280
I can’t wait to see that loser.

221
00:11:16,280 --> 00:11:19,000
Everyone, that coward Guan Feng

222
00:11:19,030 --> 00:11:22,400
was so scared of Mr. Yin...

223
00:11:22,400 --> 00:11:23,180
What are you doing?

224
00:11:23,180 --> 00:11:24,400
That he...

225
00:11:24,400 --> 00:11:25,550
What are you doing?

226
00:11:25,550 --> 00:11:27,320
-Wet his pants.
-I want to hear more!

227
00:11:27,320 --> 00:11:28,910
And he shivered in his sleep.

228
00:11:28,910 --> 00:11:31,400
Hadn’t I heard

229
00:11:31,400 --> 00:11:32,830
the made-up story,

230
00:11:35,000 --> 00:11:36,800
I wouldn’t have lost control of myself.

231
00:11:38,880 --> 00:11:40,040
You lost control

232
00:11:41,840 --> 00:11:44,020
so you held that boy hostage

233
00:11:45,000 --> 00:11:46,970
to force his father to battle you.

234
00:11:47,700 --> 00:11:55,140
(Shanchan Temple)

235
00:12:19,400 --> 00:12:20,570
Father.

236
00:12:25,230 --> 00:12:26,850
Are you that boy?

237
00:12:31,030 --> 00:12:31,620
Master,

238
00:12:32,280 --> 00:12:33,000
bad news!

239
00:12:49,380 --> 00:12:52,340
(Your son Yin Pei is in my hands...)

240
00:12:52,340 --> 00:12:54,020
(Ji Yunchen)

241
00:13:00,110 --> 00:13:01,170
Bring me the sword.

242
00:13:01,760 --> 00:13:02,550
Yes.

243
00:13:02,550 --> 00:13:06,090
My father could destroy you

244
00:13:06,710 --> 00:13:08,880
even if he was injured.

245
00:13:16,320 --> 00:13:16,920
That’s right.

246
00:13:18,960 --> 00:13:20,670
I wasn’t his match.

247
00:13:50,080 --> 00:13:50,830
Mr. Ji,

248
00:13:51,470 --> 00:13:52,590
I didn’t expect

249
00:13:53,230 --> 00:13:54,960
you’d go so low

250
00:13:54,960 --> 00:13:55,800
just to challenge me.

251
00:13:56,640 --> 00:13:59,390
My master’s reputation can’t be ruined.

252
00:14:00,080 --> 00:14:00,840
Today,

253
00:14:01,470 --> 00:14:04,080
I’m here to defend the North Blade.

254
00:14:56,350 --> 00:14:58,910
I didn’t know until later

255
00:14:58,910 --> 00:15:00,580
that he just drove those Demons away

256
00:15:01,550 --> 00:15:04,230
before I picked a fight.

257
00:15:04,230 --> 00:15:05,720
He was already injured

258
00:15:06,470 --> 00:15:08,110
but had to come

259
00:15:08,110 --> 00:15:09,670
under my threat.

260
00:15:09,670 --> 00:15:10,930
When we fought,

261
00:15:12,670 --> 00:15:14,100
he could’ve killed me.

262
00:15:20,080 --> 00:15:22,400
I’d accept

263
00:15:22,400 --> 00:15:23,960
whatever the result was.

264
00:15:23,960 --> 00:15:25,470
I could start over

265
00:15:25,470 --> 00:15:26,960
in ten years.

266
00:15:27,880 --> 00:15:28,760
But

267
00:15:29,200 --> 00:15:31,280
by breaking your sword,

268
00:15:31,280 --> 00:15:33,260
you’re insulting me!

269
00:15:35,840 --> 00:15:36,850
Mr. Ji,

270
00:15:38,000 --> 00:15:39,220
you’ll have to go through thick and thin

271
00:15:39,960 --> 00:15:42,560
in the years to come.

272
00:15:44,320 --> 00:15:45,500
I simply don’t want

273
00:15:46,280 --> 00:15:47,410
young men like you

274
00:15:48,110 --> 00:15:49,980
to die in my hands for nothing.

275
00:15:51,790 --> 00:15:53,300
Master, Master!

276
00:15:54,200 --> 00:15:55,520
Help!

277
00:15:55,520 --> 00:15:56,840
We’re under attack!

278
00:15:56,840 --> 00:15:57,590
What?

279
00:15:57,590 --> 00:15:59,230
While you lured my father out,

280
00:15:59,230 --> 00:16:00,460
those monsters broke in

281
00:16:00,960 --> 00:16:02,640
and slaughtered my whole family!

282
00:16:03,200 --> 00:16:05,000
A hundred of them

283
00:16:05,000 --> 00:16:06,600
were killed!

284
00:16:07,840 --> 00:16:09,690
Why are you still alive?

285
00:16:10,110 --> 00:16:12,350
Why aren’t you dead?

286
00:16:13,320 --> 00:16:14,260
Father!

287
00:16:15,470 --> 00:16:16,690
Father!

