You’re a Guardian, huh?

579
00:33:27,160 --> 00:33:28,880
I bet

580
00:33:28,880 --> 00:33:30,400
even Mu Xiaoqiao is better than you.

581
00:33:32,560 --> 00:33:33,770
Who are you?

582
00:33:36,950 --> 00:33:37,760
Take a guess.

583
00:33:39,160 --> 00:33:42,340
I guess you’re about to meet your doom!

584
00:33:49,830 --> 00:33:50,830
Watch it!

585
00:33:50,830 --> 00:33:52,800
I can cut off the heavenly river.

586
00:33:52,800 --> 00:33:54,640
Don’t blink.

587
00:34:14,520 --> 00:34:15,470
Seize her!

588
00:34:27,320 --> 00:34:28,800
A one-on-one with Dragon Master?

589
00:34:28,800 --> 00:34:31,000
What were you thinking?

590
00:34:31,000 --> 00:34:32,840
Didn’t you pull me up?

591
00:34:34,470 --> 00:34:36,150
Hadn’t it been for his palm,

592
00:34:36,150 --> 00:34:37,100
you wouldn’t have

593
00:34:38,280 --> 00:34:40,000
had such strength.

594
00:34:42,120 --> 00:34:43,910
Should I thank him for that?

595
00:34:45,390 --> 00:34:47,180
My skills have improved a lot.

596
00:34:54,280 --> 00:34:55,520
Stop laughing!

597
00:34:58,950 --> 00:35:01,050
As odd as he seems,

598
00:35:01,760 --> 00:35:03,830
I still trust him for no reason.

599
00:35:06,080 --> 00:35:08,120
Is it because of his look?

600
00:35:13,190 --> 00:35:14,950
Are you messing with me?

601
00:35:14,950 --> 00:35:17,040
Wait after we get out of here.

602
00:35:27,080 --> 00:35:28,390
What are you looking for?

603
00:35:29,910 --> 00:35:31,330
The secret tunnel should be nearby.

604
00:35:31,870 --> 00:35:33,370
It’s concealed though.

605
00:35:36,360 --> 00:35:38,630
Fei! Fei!

606
00:35:40,950 --> 00:35:41,760
Come here!

607
00:36:20,150 --> 00:36:21,390
Should I call you bold or stupid?

608
00:36:25,280 --> 00:36:25,950
Where’s your blade?

609
00:36:30,360 --> 00:36:31,360
None of your own business.

610
00:36:32,040 --> 00:36:34,950
You fought against Dragon Master
barehanded.

611
00:36:34,950 --> 00:36:35,600
That’s...

612
00:36:40,840 --> 00:36:42,000
I’ve got nothing

613
00:36:42,000 --> 00:36:43,520
other than this.

614
00:36:43,520 --> 00:36:44,470
Make do with it.

615
00:36:45,840 --> 00:36:47,560
Where did you get this?

616
00:36:47,560 --> 00:36:48,760
Is it to brace yourself up?

617
00:36:49,430 --> 00:36:50,870
I found it just now.

618
00:36:52,630 --> 00:36:53,950
You can think up

619
00:36:53,950 --> 00:36:54,800
all kinds of ways

620
00:36:54,800 --> 00:36:56,600
to mock your own people.

621
00:36:57,280 --> 00:36:58,390
But when it comes to

622
00:36:58,390 --> 00:36:59,950
life and death,

623
00:36:59,950 --> 00:37:01,190
you can only talk with your fists.

624
00:37:01,190 --> 00:37:03,190
Can you think first next time?

625
00:37:05,080 --> 00:37:07,040
-You... You...
-Fei.

626
00:37:07,040 --> 00:37:08,320
Stop arguing.

627
00:37:09,430 --> 00:37:12,000
Don’t act rashly again.

628
00:37:12,470 --> 00:37:13,280
But...

629
00:37:13,280 --> 00:37:15,150
We’re worried about you.

630
00:37:15,150 --> 00:37:15,910
I...

631
00:37:16,120 --> 00:37:17,430
Isn’t he safe and sound?

632
00:37:17,430 --> 00:37:18,870
So am I.

633
00:37:18,870 --> 00:37:21,760
Yes, you returned intact,

634
00:37:21,760 --> 00:37:24,630
but not your blade.

635
00:37:28,230 --> 00:37:29,390
Once I’m back,

636
00:37:29,390 --> 00:37:31,840
I’ll make you a bag

637
00:37:33,150 --> 00:37:36,230
with multiple pouches around

638
00:37:36,230 --> 00:37:37,360
for blades.

639
00:37:37,360 --> 00:37:39,080
You can carry it

640
00:37:39,080 --> 00:37:40,800
like a peacock spreading its tail.

641
00:37:40,800 --> 00:37:42,450
How nice and convenient that is!

642
00:37:43,230 --> 00:37:44,630
You won’t be short of weapons again.

643
00:37:47,470 --> 00:37:48,630
Where are you going?

644
00:37:53,870 --> 00:37:54,500
I’m going to...

645
00:37:59,230 --> 00:38:00,870
to... The Fortress
of the Forty-Eight with you.

646
00:38:04,870 --> 00:38:06,150
Let’s go.

647
00:38:06,840 --> 00:38:08,840
Come on, Fei.

648
00:38:33,430 --> 00:38:35,120
There are signs of struggle.

649
00:38:40,040 --> 00:38:42,520
Dragon Master must be badly injured.

650
00:38:42,520 --> 00:38:43,920
We can rest inside for now

651
00:38:44,360 --> 00:38:45,840
until he leaves.

652
00:39:01,320 --> 00:39:02,800
Is this the Forbidden Hall
of the Qi School?

653
00:39:04,840 --> 00:39:06,890
Go get some clean water.

654
00:39:08,320 --> 00:39:09,090
What for?

655
00:39:09,560 --> 00:39:11,020
You don’t need to know.

656
00:39:53,080 --> 00:39:55,560
No one

657
00:39:55,560 --> 00:39:57,120
can get in or out

658
00:39:57,120 --> 00:39:58,470
without filling that bowl

659
00:39:58,470 --> 00:39:59,680
with water.

660
00:40:00,910 --> 00:40:01,720
Impressive!

661
00:40:02,190 --> 00:40:04,080
Follow me.

662
00:40:18,840 --> 00:40:20,390
-Miss Zhou. Miss Wu.
-Mr. Ji.

663
00:40:20,390 --> 00:40:21,360
And Xiao...

664
00:40:21,910 --> 00:40:24,320
I lied to them.

665
00:40:24,320 --> 00:40:25,440
Call me Xie Yun.

666
00:40:26,670 --> 00:40:27,870
Mr. Xie,

667
00:40:27,870 --> 00:40:30,000
what is it about the Mountain Sword

668
00:40:30,000 --> 00:40:30,780
that you told Dragon Master?

669
00:40:31,560 --> 00:40:32,990
He probably made that up.

670
00:40:38,760 --> 00:40:39,470
Sorry.

671
00:40:39,470 --> 00:40:41,670
I lied to him.

672
00:40:43,800 --> 00:40:46,080
But I did hear things

673
00:40:46,630 --> 00:40:47,930
that might or might not be true.

674
00:40:48,630 --> 00:40:49,370
What do you know?

675
00:40:51,230 --> 00:40:52,520
It’s said that

676
00:40:52,520 --> 00:40:54,520
when the South Blade
was hunted by Demons,

677
00:40:56,280 --> 00:40:57,870
he fought and ran

678
00:40:58,360 --> 00:41:00,650
but was almost caught more than once.

679
00:41:01,000 --> 00:41:02,690
Then unexpectedly,

680
00:41:05,760 --> 00:41:07,170
he destroyed his weapon.

681
00:41:11,360 --> 00:41:12,760
Is that true?

682
00:41:14,120 --> 00:41:15,980
Why did I hear nothing from my father?

683
00:41:17,710 --> 00:41:19,150
I don’t

684
00:41:19,150 --> 00:41:20,790
get that, either.

685
00:41:21,910 --> 00:41:22,560
Think about it.

686
00:41:23,040 --> 00:41:24,190
When someone is

687
00:41:24,190 --> 00:41:25,330
after you,

688
00:41:25,910 --> 00:41:27,360
will you destroy your weapon

689
00:41:27,360 --> 00:41:30,190
instead of trying to escape?

690
00:41:30,190 --> 00:41:31,240
Of course not.

691
00:41:34,320 --> 00:41:36,070
Then those blabbermouths

692
00:41:36,800 --> 00:41:39,110
spread rumors

693
00:41:39,760 --> 00:41:41,360
about some evil magic

694
00:41:41,360 --> 00:41:43,190
that as long as

695
00:41:43,190 --> 00:41:45,630
one obtained a master’s weapon,

696
00:41:45,630 --> 00:41:48,150
he could gain that person’s skills.

697
00:41:52,320 --> 00:41:54,040
That’s bullcrap.

698
00:41:54,040 --> 00:41:55,440
Utter nonsense.

699
00:41:56,710 --> 00:41:58,910
Mr. Ji is unsuspecting.

700
00:41:58,910 --> 00:42:00,060
He seems to be convinced.

701
00:42:01,950 --> 00:42:03,520
Don’t look at me, Mr. Ji.

702
00:42:03,520 --> 00:42:05,000
That’s just what I heard.

703
00:42:05,000 --> 00:42:06,800
But I did learn to cast swords

704
00:42:06,800 --> 00:42:08,300
to dig deep into it.

705
00:42:09,950 --> 00:42:11,490
How could that be possible?

706
00:42:11,800 --> 00:42:13,790
It’s baseless.

707
00:42:14,150 --> 00:42:15,710
Are you saying

708
00:42:15,710 --> 00:42:18,130
Dragon Master plotted
against Mr. Yin Wenlan

709
00:42:18,520 --> 00:42:21,110
because of such hogwash?

710
00:42:22,230 --> 00:42:23,040
About that,

711
00:42:23,710 --> 00:42:25,660
you need to ask Mr. Yin.

712
00:42:42,560 --> 00:42:43,560
Mr. Yin.

713
00:42:49,390 --> 00:42:50,950
Now, can you tell us

714
00:42:50,950 --> 00:42:52,700
why Dragon Master insists on
having you back?

715
00:43:05,040 --> 00:43:06,100
It makes sense

716
00:43:06,560 --> 00:43:09,050
that you fell out
with your foster father

717
00:43:09,320 --> 00:43:11,630
after knowing the truth

718
00:43:11,630 --> 00:43:12,540
about your family’s murder.

719
00:43:13,430 --> 00:43:14,840
What doesn’t make sense is

720
00:43:14,840 --> 00:43:16,280
you’d come all the way

721
00:43:16,630 --> 00:43:18,070
to kill a feeble man

722
00:43:18,950 --> 00:43:20,760
at the cost of exposing yourself

723
00:43:20,760 --> 00:43:22,100
after enduring years of humiliation.

724
00:43:24,390 --> 00:43:26,710
He seemed to come to stir up trouble

725
00:43:26,710 --> 00:43:28,560
with Old Dragon,

726
00:43:28,560 --> 00:43:31,470
but actually, he wanted Old Dragon dead.

727
00:43:33,560 --> 00:43:36,120
When he pretended to kill others

728
00:43:36,710 --> 00:43:38,190
but got stopped

729
00:43:38,190 --> 00:43:39,720
by your chopstick,

730
00:43:40,360 --> 00:43:41,340
he didn’t leave

731
00:43:42,000 --> 00:43:44,110
but went straight into the Sanchun Inn

732
00:43:44,320 --> 00:43:45,720
and came at you.

733
00:43:46,320 --> 00:43:47,760
He was picking a fight on purpose.

734
00:43:47,760 --> 00:43:48,160
Exactly.

735
00:43:49,670 --> 00:43:50,950
Then, of course,

736
00:43:50,950 --> 00:43:52,710
you caught him.

737
00:43:53,360 --> 00:43:54,950
Other than that,

738
00:43:54,950 --> 00:43:56,350
he kept fanning the flames

739
00:43:57,150 --> 00:43:58,350
to incite you to kill Old Dragon.

740
00:43:58,800 --> 00:44:00,080
No wonder

741
00:44:00,080 --> 00:44:01,590
he’s been clinging on to us

742
00:44:01,910 --> 00:44:03,000
without any attempt to escape.

743
00:44:04,080 --> 00:44:05,420
Later, when Dragon Master arrived

744
00:44:05,760 --> 00:44:06,980
and encountered Wen Yu,

745
00:44:07,360 --> 00:44:09,000
he managed to get out

746
00:44:11,320 --> 00:44:12,960
and planned to kidnap Miss Wu.

747
00:44:14,150 --> 00:44:15,020
That way,

748
00:44:15,560 --> 00:44:17,020
he could take advantage
of Wen Yu’s power.

749
00:44:18,000 --> 00:44:18,990
Although he failed,

750
00:44:19,470 --> 00:44:20,630
he still got out

751
00:44:20,630 --> 00:44:21,680
with us.

752
00:44:24,600 --> 00:44:25,430
Miss Zhou.

753
00:44:28,630 --> 00:44:30,670
You’re smart enough
to figure out everything.

754
00:44:30,670 --> 00:44:32,360
Why are you asking me?

755
00:44:32,360 --> 00:44:34,360
I’m not half

756
00:44:34,360 --> 00:44:35,950
as smart and calculative as you are.

757
00:44:38,190 --> 00:44:39,840
He can’t fight anymore.

758
00:44:39,840 --> 00:44:40,950
What if

759
00:44:40,950 --> 00:44:43,040
no one in the Inn could stop Old Dragon?

760
00:44:43,040 --> 00:44:43,870
Did that ever occur to you?

761
00:44:48,430 --> 00:44:49,720
Not everyone

762
00:44:50,040 --> 00:44:51,810
is as lucky as you, lass!

763
00:44:52,560 --> 00:44:55,260
You have family support and fine skills.

764
00:44:56,080 --> 00:44:57,080
You’re so spoiled

765
00:44:57,080 --> 00:44:59,040
and ignorant.

766
00:44:59,840 --> 00:45:00,840
Is that

767
00:45:00,840 --> 00:45:03,320
a complaint or a compliment?

768
00:45:04,230 --> 00:45:06,000
Without Ji Yunchen,

769
00:45:06,000 --> 00:45:08,080
I would’ve become the heir

770
00:45:08,080 --> 00:45:09,330
to the Mountain Sword.

771
00:45:10,190 --> 00:45:12,470
You wouldn’t even get to lick my boots!

772
00:45:12,470 --> 00:45:13,190
What did you say?

773
00:45:13,190 --> 00:45:14,320
You heard me!

774
00:45:14,760 --> 00:45:15,130
You...

775
00:45:16,910 --> 00:45:18,450
Don’t mind it.

776
00:45:23,600 --> 00:45:25,120
Yes, what could’ve happened?

777
00:45:25,950 --> 00:45:28,080
The worst case would be Ji Yunchen

778
00:45:28,080 --> 00:45:29,710
and some unlucky man

779
00:45:29,710 --> 00:45:31,870
died in Old Dragon’s hands.

780
00:45:31,870 --> 00:45:33,180
What was that to do with us?

781
00:45:33,840 --> 00:45:36,370
So you could easily tell him

782
00:45:36,710 --> 00:45:38,140
that Ji Yunchen was your enemy.

783
00:45:38,670 --> 00:45:40,120
That wouldn’t raise any suspicion

784
00:45:40,120 --> 00:45:41,560
as the good and the evil

785
00:45:41,560 --> 00:45:42,910
were born to be foes.

786
00:45:42,910 --> 00:45:44,800
Old Dragon wouldn’t suspect a thing.

787
00:45:44,800 --> 00:45:46,670
If he killed Ji Yunchen,

788
00:45:46,670 --> 00:45:48,580
that’d only boost his ego.

789
00:45:49,000 --> 00:45:50,410
Because never did he know

790
00:45:50,600 --> 00:45:51,480
that you’re a Yin,

791
00:45:51,800 --> 00:45:52,850
nor would he ever expect

792
00:45:53,230 --> 00:45:54,320
that you wouldn’t

793
00:45:54,710 --> 00:45:56,310
go back after this.

794
00:46:04,110 --> 00:46:07,620
♪Stars flow like river♪

795
00:46:08,680 --> 00:46:12,280
♪My yearning falls into the river♪

796
00:46:12,850 --> 00:46:16,920
♪Now that you’re in my life♪

797
00:46:17,170 --> 00:46:20,810
♪I will never be alone♪

798
00:46:20,810 --> 00:46:24,930
♪I haven’t seen the mountains with you♪

799
00:46:25,350 --> 00:46:29,780
♪Nor have I tied up your hair♪

800
00:46:30,440 --> 00:46:35,000
♪We haven’t finished our story in chaos♪

801
00:46:35,230 --> 00:46:39,860
♪The blade hasn’t been returned♪

802
00:46:40,050 --> 00:46:43,880
♪I fear not to roam the world with you♪

803
00:46:44,100 --> 00:46:48,790
♪When I go across the world for you♪

804
00:46:49,050 --> 00:46:52,790
♪I’m willing to shed blood for you♪

805
00:46:53,120 --> 00:46:58,210
♪Don’t mind whose land it is♪

806
00:46:58,210 --> 00:47:02,150
♪Where is home to the snowflake♪

807
00:47:02,150 --> 00:47:06,680
♪Come and melt in my embrace♪

808
00:47:07,300 --> 00:47:14,400
♪The spring sun is an invisible armor
that’ll hold♪

809
00:47:15,140 --> 00:47:19,770
♪The purest love is unadorned♪
